== Intro ==
[[image:InfRubyCompanyScreenshot]]

Auto-completion for Inf-Ruby (IRB) buffers.

NOTE: This has been obsoleted by [https://github.com/company-mode/company-inf-ruby company-inf-ruby]. -- DmitryGutov

== Download ==
[http://gist.github.com/raw/610104/b4db1e8789d8507d00b7d56672485143e9eec72c/inf-ruby-company.el inf-ruby-company.el]

[http://gist.github.com/610104 Gist page]

== Installation ==
1. Install [[CompanyMode]] and get the latest inf-ruby via [http://marmalade-repo.org/packages/inf-ruby package.el] or [http://github.com/nonsequitur/inf-ruby/raw/master//inf-ruby.el GitHub]

2. Add Inf-Ruby-Company to your load path, like

   (add-to-list 'load-path "<directory that includes inf-ruby-company>")

2. Add the following to your Emacs setup:

   (add-hook 'inf-ruby-mode-hook (lambda () (require 'inf-ruby-company)))

== Tweak Company Mode for instant completion ==
   (setq company-idle-delay 0.1)
   (setq company-minimum-prefix-length 2)

